high_descs: Walk over to the chair in the corner of the room, then turn right to face the wooden table.
Pick up the closest butter knife off of the wooden table
Turn right and walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk over to the fridge, hang a right and walk towards the counter, turn right before you get there to face the counter.
Put the butter knife in the wooden cup on the counter.
Pick up the wooden cup with the knife in it off of the counter.
Turn right and walk back over to the wooden table.
Put the wooden cup with the butter knife in it on the wooden table to the left of the closest loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a wooden cup with a butter knife in it on the wooden table.

high_descs: Go straight to the chair in the corner and turn right towards the table.
Pick up the knife that is to the right of the potato.
Turn to the right, then go left towards the fridge, make a right towards the dishwasher and turn right towards the cup on the counter.
Put the knife in the cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup with the knife in it.
Turn right towards the fridge, turn left and head back to the table on the right.
Put the cup to the left of the bread and potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a cup on the table.

high_descs: Walk forward to the chair then turn right.
Pick up the butter knife that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk a few steps then turn left and walk to the fridge then turn right and walk to the orange cup on the counter to your right.
Put the knife in the orange cup.
Pick up the orange cup with the knife in it.
Go back to where you got the knife.
Put the cup to the left of the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife it it on the table.
